  title `The Representation of the People Act, 1951`
  actNumber (43)
  enactmentDate 1951-07-17
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/2096`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `लोकप्रतिनिधित्वअधिनियम, 1951`
  actYear (1951)
  ministry `Ministry of Law and Justice`
  department `Legislative Department`
  longTitle `An Act to provide for the conduct of elections to the Houses of Parliament and to the House or Houses of the Legislature of each State, the qualifications and disqualifications for membership of those Houses, the corrupt practices and other offences at or in connection with such elections and the decision of doubts and disputes arising out of or in connection with such elections.`
